{"tid":2311664,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"月入高達$12000  大學畢業生啟航計劃 2000個機會 乞食科福音","createTime":"2020-12-04T08:46:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T11:36:19.000Z","uid":248054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"99f97e645dde831c100bd617c62cfc2e5c8cb009","tid":2311664,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:46:44.000Z","msg":"疫情重創本港經濟，失業率不斷創新高，大學生一畢業就可能要失業。香港中國企業協會推出「青春試翼●大學畢業生啟航計劃」，為近兩年畢業的大學生提供逾2,000個為期6個月或以上職位，計劃由勞工處提供支援。"},{"pid":"1ac204a21f0b5e00122e8dba2c7a963e15066927","tid":2311664,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:47:16.000Z","msg":"所有在2019或2020年於香港或以外院校完成學士或以上學位課程的香港居民均合資格申請，在計劃下可獲得不低於1.2萬元月薪，當中包括不同行業，如銀行、金融、進出口貿易、資訊科技、通訊及物流業，職位類別亦包括培訓實習生、助理經理、分析員、工程師、程序員、測量師及會計師等。<br />\n<br />\n翻閱該計劃網站，目前已有不同行業的職位可供申請，主要是中資公司在香港的企業提供職位，香港中國企業協會稱有超過200間協會轄下的會員機構參與。"},{"pid":"1bf7f3d77d29672a7fc63c572402ad68bba1553a","tid":2311664,"uid":248054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:47:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://job.hkcea.com/?iswap=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjob.hkcea.com%2F%3Fiswap%3D1&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGOSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=5b68441c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://job.hkcea.com/?iswap=1</a>"},{"pid":"883b7bc46e0b03903fa13a7d4757e6d345b8627c","tid":2311664,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MfUu4LF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMfUu4LF.jpg&h=900afc67&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c6de3466330ad6248315b8ab305dfa1caadbf65","tid":2311664,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:55:27.000Z","msg":"反全球化最中意嘅工作機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3d21f93c21191e2affa019cc403f1da3205dd0","tid":2311664,"uid":171475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":